1. Ctrl+` to open terminal.
2. Click the three expandable list upper right corner of the command window. Select command prompt.
3. Type npm run start:dev:safe (A new script to make sure the address is not in use)
4. Open browser in one of these ways:
   a. Press Ctrl+Shift+P, type "Browser" and select the browser option
   b. Or manually open Chrome/Edge/Firefox and navigate to http://localhost:3000
   c. Or check View menu for "Browser" option (may need Cursor restart if missing)


